&lt;p&gt;Update #2: Download from Huawei AppGallery: &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://appgallery.huawei.com/app/C105053423&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
